STATE
v.
SYKES 2019-0058 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 29, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

RECONSIDERATION OF PRIOR DECISIONS

On motion for reconsideration. Motion denied. Appellee's motion to strike appellant's motion for reconsideration denied. French and Stewart, JJ., concur in part and dissent in part and would grant appellant's motion for reconsideration. Donnelly, J., not participating.
